(1, '🏠 Managing Property in Kenya Just Got Smarter — Introducing RentSmart', '🏠 Managing Property in Kenya Just Got Smarter — Introducing RentSmart', 'Dear <strong>{name}</strong>\r\n\r\nIf you own or manage rental property in Kenya, you already know the headaches: late rent payments, tenant disputes, lost records, and the endless back-and-forth between landlords, agents, and property managers.\r\n\r\nThat\'s exactly why we built RentSmart.\r\n🏢 WHAT IS RENTSMART?\r\nRentSmart is a modern property management platform built specifically for the Kenyan real estate market. Whether you\'re a landlord with a single block of flats or a property manager handling a portfolio of properties, RentSmart puts everything in one place.\r\n\r\n✅ WHAT RENTSMART DOES FOR YOU\r\n\r\n📋 Tenant Management\r\nOnboard tenants digitally, store lease agreements, and track occupancy — all from your phone or computer.\r\n\r\n💳 Rent Collection & Tracking\r\nSend automated rent reminders and track payments in real time. No more chasing tenants manually.\r\n\r\n🧾 Financial Reports\r\nGenerate income statements, payment histories, and arrears reports instantly — perfect for landlords who want full financial visibility.\r\n\r\n🔑 Multi-Role Access\r\nRentSmart supports four user roles — Landlord, Property Manager, Agent, and Realtor — each with their own dashboard and permissions tailored to their work.\r\n\r\n📱 Mobile-Friendly\r\nAccess your property data anytime, anywhere, straight from your smartphone.\r\n\r\n💡 WHY PROPERTY PROFESSIONALS LOVE IT\r\n\r\n\"I used to spend hours every month chasing rent and updating spreadsheets. RentSmart handles it all — I just log in and everything is there.\"\r\n— Property Manager, Nairobi\r\n\r\n🚀 GET STARTED TODAY\r\n\r\nWe\'re currently onboarding new property managers and landlords across Kenya. Whether you manage 5 units or 500, RentSmart scales with you.\r\n\r\nBook a Free Demo\r\n👉 Visit Our Website: https://rentsmart.timestentechnologies.co.ke/\r\n👉 Call / WhatsApp: +254795155230\r\n\r\nWe\'d love to show you how RentSmart can save you time, reduce losses, and bring order to your property management.\r\n\r\nWarm regards,\r\nRentSmart\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:30px;\"><img src=\"https://rentsmart.timestentechnologies.co.ke/public/assets/images/site_logo_1751627446.png\" alt=\"Rent Smart Kenya Logo\" style=\"max-width:200px;max-height:80px;\"></div>\r\n\r\nYou\'re receiving this because you\'re a property professional in Kenya. To unsubscribe, reply with \"STOP\".', 'newsletter', 'draft', NULL, '2026-03-17 20:47:04', 9, 9, 0, 0, 1, '2026-03-17 06:13:41', '2026-03-17 20:33:31');
